data.description: Step into refined Lowcountry living with this meticulously crafted residence. The interior opens to a formal dining room that sets the tone for sophisticated gatherings. The heart of the home lies in the spacious kitchen, a culinary haven with an abundance of cabinet space. Adjacent to the kitchen, the family room is a warm and welcoming space, ideal for everyday comfort and relaxation. Discover an oversized master bedroom, the ensuite bathroom, complemented by a walk-in closet, offers a perfect balance of luxury and practicality. Step outside to the large fenced backyard, that offers beautiful water views.
